"""
        Test of :meth:`PyTravisCI.communication.Communication.get_url_of_next_page`.
        """
response_without_pagination = {'@type': 'home', '@href': '/', 'errors': {
    'login_required': {'status': 403, 'default_message': 'login required',
    'additional_attributes': []}, 'method_not_allowed': {'status': 405,
    'default_message': 'method not allowed', 'additional_attributes': []},
    'not_found': {'status': 404, 'default_message':
    'resource not found (or insufficient access)', 'additional_attributes':
    ['resource_type']}}}
comm = Communication(self.root)
expected = None
actual = comm.get_url_of_next_page(response_without_pagination)
self.assertEqual(expected, actual)
response_with_pagination = {'@type': 'branches', '@href':
    '/repo/891/branches?exists_on_github=true&limit=5', '@representation':
    'standard', '@pagination': {'limit': 5, 'offset': 0, 'count': 24,
    'is_first': True, 'is_last': False, 'next': {'@href':
    '/repo/891/branches?exists_on_github=true&limit=5&offset=5', 'offset': 
    5, 'limit': 5}, 'prev': None, 'first': {'@href':
    '/repo/891/branches?exists_on_github=true&limit=5', 'offset': 0,
    'limit': 5}, 'last': {'@href':
    '/repo/891/branches?exists_on_github=true&limit=5&offset=20', 'offset':
    20, 'limit': 5}}}
expected = (
    f'{AccessPoints.OPEN}/repo/891/branches?exists_on_github=true&limit=5&offset=5'
    )
actual = comm.get_url_of_next_page(response_with_pagination)
self.assertEqual(expected, actual)
